  "title": "🌟 Retail Supervisor / Assistant Store Manager (Bookstore) | Up to 3.5K |",
  "description": "<p><strong>Salary:</strong></p><ul><li>Gross Monthly Salary: $2,800 – $3,500</li></ul><p><strong>Working Hours:</strong></p><ul><li>44hrs/week</li></ul><p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Supervise and coordinate daily store operations, including staff scheduling, task allocation, and performance monitoring</li><li>Provide excellent customer service by assisting customers, handling enquiries, and resolving issues professionally</li><li>Ensure store standards are maintained across operations, inventory control, and visual merchandising</li><li>Identify and implement initiatives to improve store efficiency, sales performance, and customer satisfaction</li><li>Work closely with the store management team to support marketing campaigns and in-store promotions</li><li>Guide, coach, and support team members to achieve operational and service standards</li></ul><p><strong>Job Requirements</strong></p><ul><li>3–5 years of retail experience, including at least 2 years in a supervisory or leadership role</li><li>Strong customer service orientation and ability to handle customer interactions effectively</li><li>Good communication, interpersonal, and leadership skills</li><li>Experience in inventory management, merchandising, and retail operations</li><li>Ability to work flexible schedules, including weekends and public holidays, based on operational needs</li><li>Good problem-solving and decision-making skills</li><li>Interest in the retail industry and commitment to delivering quality service</li></ul><p></p><p><em>Only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</em><br /></p><p><strong>Chan Qing Yuan Tricia</strong></p><p><strong>Outsourcing Team</strong></p><p><strong>HRnet Ventures Pte Ltd – CREW by HRnet</strong></p><p><strong>E.A. 24C2435</strong></p>",
